{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, we propose an LAoT model caching algorithm based on the concept of AoT where the model with the least valuable thoughts is evicted.The maximum token consumption for each CoT step is set to 200 in the experiment.",
    "The context window of LLaMA is 4K tokens, the context window of GPT-3.5-turbo is 16K tokens, and the context window of GPT-4 is 32K tokens.",
    "We consider an edge server with 64 GPUs with 80 GB memory, 312 TFLOPS, and 300W max thermal design power.",
    "We consider 30 types of services and 10 edge LLM agents.",
    "The experimental results are illustrated in Fig. 3."
  ]
}